thread.title_full: Lucky Tackle Box reviewed by Kawidaddy 710

author: Kawidaddy 710
title: Kawidaddy 710
text: The energy and style Travis gives off in the videos is awesome. It makes learning new fishing techniques fun and easy. My BassXL box was missing the "Golden Ticket" the other day. I emailed LTB and Andrew S. replied quite quickly. Before I knew it,he sent a "virtual" Golden Ticket to my email. Thanks Andrew S for the prompt and helpful reply. Love LTB
